    when the token exchange fails
      redirects to login with the error message

Integration Flows
  Full webhook flow: POST → ConversationHandler → WhatsApp response
    receives webhook, enqueues job, and routes to ProviderAssistant
  Onboarding flow: unknown number → registration → Provider created
    when unknown number sends first message
      sends welcome message and stores onboarding state
    when user responds with '2' to register
      routes to OnboardingService
  Job registration flow: provider message → Job + Transaction created
    creates Job and Transaction records when provider reports completed work
  Client appointment flow: short_uuid → Appointment created → Provider notified
    creates Appointment when client books through short_uuid
  Review request flow: Job paid → ReviewRequestJob enqueued → Review created
    creates Review when client responds with rating
  Facebook OAuth flow: connect_token → OAuth → token saved
    validates connect_token and redirects to Facebook OAuth
    exchanges code for token and saves to provider
  Message persistence: trivial vs. critical intent
    when message is trivial
      does not persist the message
    when message has critical intent
      persists the message

