Assistants::EscalationDetector
  .call
    when body is blank
      returns no escalation
    when single-word danger keywords are detected
      detects 'humo' as danger
      detects 'quemado' as danger
      detects 'chispas' as danger
      detects 'cortocircuito' as danger
      detects 'incendio' as danger
      detects 'fuego' as danger
      detects 'derrumbe' as danger
      detects 'emergencia' as danger
      detects 'peligro' as danger
      detects 'auxilio' as danger
      detects 'ambulancia' as danger
      detects 'bomberos' as danger
      detects 'accidente' as danger
    when multi-word danger phrases are detected
      detects 'fuga de gas' as danger
      detects 'olor a quemado' as danger
      detects 'fuga de agua' as danger
      detects 'no puedo respirar' as danger
      detects 'ayuda urgente' as danger
    when short keywords appear inside unrelated words
      does not detect 'gas' inside 'gastos'
    when speak-with-person patterns are detected
      detects 'hablar con una persona' as speak_with_person
      detects 'necesito hablar con alguien' as speak_with_person
      detects 'persona real' as speak_with_person
    when price negotiation patterns are detected
      detects 'muy caro' as price_negotiation
      detects 'más barato' as price_negotiation
      detects 'descuento' as price_negotiation
      detects 'no me alcanza' as price_negotiation
    when complaint patterns are detected
      detects 'mal trabajo' as complaint
      detects 'quedó mal' as complaint
      detects 'no sirve' as complaint
      detects 'reclamo' as complaint
    when no escalation triggers are present
      returns no escalation for normal messages
  .escalate!
    updates conversation stage to escalated
    sends escalation message to provider
    includes client phone in escalation message
    builds complaint message for complaint reason
    builds angry client message

